            <h1>AdventureWorks Sales Analysis Using SQL</h1>

            <p>
                Performed SQL-based exploratory sales analysis using the
                AdventureWorks database to uncover revenue trends,
                identify top-performing products, analyze regional sales
                performance, and apply advanced SQL techniques including
                joins, aggregations, and window functions.
            </p>

